<item>
<title>我们困扰于信息过载时，却有孩子连基本精神食粮都得不到</title>
<link>http://www.jintiankansha.me/t/HM490ME0mE</link>
<guid isPermaLink="true" >http://www.jintiankansha.me/t/HM490ME0mE</guid>
<description>&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; justify=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;张佳玮说：&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; justify=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;我们住在大城市的许多人，可能身处信息过载模式——信息太多，无从选择，在一个应用到另一个应用之间急速跳跃，大口大口吞咽五光十色、新鲜出炉的文化产品。&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; justify=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;然而撑的撑死，饿的饿死。&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; justify=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;这片土地上，还有许多孩子，连基本的精神食粮都没有。我们知道这一点，但往往无能为力：我们的触角，还伸不到那里。&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; justify=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;所以如果有触角可以将最新的东西伸到那里，总会好一些。&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;hr /&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; center=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;给云南昭通镇雄县店子小学&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;三年级学生&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; center=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;卢雨泽的一封信&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; justify=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;卢雨泽，你好吗？&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; justify=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;上次见面我给你讲了“星期五”的故事，你很喜欢，后来我推荐了《鲁滨逊漂流记》给你，不知道你读到哪里了？“星期五”出现了吗？&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; justify=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;我还记得第一次知道你的情景。那是一个周六，妈妈带我去看一部叫《三只小猪》的环保儿童剧，听妈妈说除了能看表演，现场还能用旧书换新书，帮助偏远地区没有课外书的小朋友。从小到大，妈妈每年都会给我买很多书，有《十万个为什么》、《格林童话》、《海底两万里》，看完的书已经在家里堆成一座小山了，我不知道该拿它们怎么办……我很想帮助那些没有书看的小朋友，于是特意挑选了《假如给我三天光明》、《格列佛游记》两本书带去。等到换书的时候，我才知道这些书都是为你和你的同学收集的，也知道了你们那么渴望一本课外书！妈妈告诉我，全国还有两千多个像我这样的小朋友也为你们捐了课外书，一共有四千多本呢，这下你再也不用怕没有课外书看了！&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; center=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.66640625&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;1280&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/1xFs3zCgicXgxC7Jv2ibczolSbuzrrPdUwibYYCznt7andmKyhmJkIw5G0Llzo5uJPwSC94D8lvnbpl2VYe9icaIEQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; center=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;全国十城的小朋友在环保公益儿童剧巡演现场捐赠闲置童书&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; justify=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;后来，我和妈妈还被选为爱心家庭的代表，和“绿动未来”的志愿者叔叔阿姨们一起给你的学校建了环保公益图书馆。我们就是在你那天见面的！虽然你的学校操场没有草坪、教室里的课桌也旧旧的，但那天和你一起看书讲故事，我真的很开心！&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; center=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.6542721518987342&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;1264&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/1xFs3zCgicXgxC7Jv2ibczolSbuzrrPdUwUTRPZibM7Yx97Ivoy7I0Kk2BrlcaVIFlRNicW8Jzxs87jDesgBzNc38A/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; center=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;“绿动未来环保公益图书馆”与“绿动未来环保公益实践基地”落成&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; center=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.64375&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;1280&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/1xFs3zCgicXgxC7Jv2ibczolSbuzrrPdUwCFQqM72L6zsibMia0ciabwVB01QQzib5o5f0FLSv7NEkEFm3zzYP1msLOA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; center=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;ins class=&quot;adsbygoogle&quot; data-ad-layout=&quot;in-article&quot; data-ad-format=&quot;fluid&quot; data-ad-client=&quot;ca-pub-1837452791782084&quot; data-ad-slot=&quot;7041996284&quot;&gt;&lt;/ins&gt; &lt;span&gt;大家迫不及待地排队进入“绿动未来”环保公益图书馆&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

